<br>
Chanters would bitch/moan/complain cause we're turning into something else, that they should get the spell...<br>
<br>
Druids/Shamans/Bards would bitch/moan/complain because sow just isn't fast enough anymore.<br>
<br>
Here's what it would take to get the spell live.  Spell duration would be based on stamina - or - 20 seconds.  You would have falling damage if you flew off a ledge (read, use levitate).  It would have a 30 second cast time, with a 5 minute recast time.  And, it would cost 500mana.  There's no way in hell they'd give this to us.  It doesn't fit in &quot;The Vision (tm)&quot;.<br>
<br>
But that's not to say it wouldn't kick arse.  I am Magic, in its purest form.  I should be able to change myself into any form I please, and do anything I please, because I AM Magic.  However, if we were &quot;true&quot; wizards, we wouldn't have any other classes being played, because nothing would be able to stop us.  I like the idea, but it'll never happen like you want it to.  Wonder how that exact sentence applies to the familiars... <p></p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/ugoramon.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Goramon</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC=http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/black_redspot.gif BORDER=0> at: 8/21/01 6:16:32 am<br></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/uakkronn.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Akkronn</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC=http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/black_lightning.gif BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Apprentice</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(8/17/01 8:41:32 am)</font><br>    <BR><img src=c:\temp\Wizardpic.gif WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Yonder</span><hr size=1> before trying to think what other class whi do just try to put a good idea first. <br>
